%package devel_yast
%pattern_development
Summary:        YaST Development
Group:          Metapackages
Provides:       pattern() = devel_yast
Provides:       pattern-icon() = pattern-yast-devel
Provides:       pattern-order() = 3460
Provides:       pattern-visible()

Recommends:     yast2-devtools
